    "C. Previous seminal work for updating traditional STS theoryThe research and application of STS theory have been carried out for decades [97].",
    "Over time, its emphasis has shifted from an early focus on heavy industry [33] to advanced manufacturing technologies [40] and then to office-based workplace services [39], [41], [42].",
    "Although the applications have evolved, the underlying philosophy of STS has remained unchanged [89].",
    "With the rise of AI technology, researchers are calling for advances in STS theory to address the unique challenges and opportunities presented in the context of AI.Below, we highlight key insights from recent research outcomes.",
    "These previous studies have provided valuable."
  ]
}